content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2108.15 - Protests against an order of the State rent administrator

State Regulations

Any person aggrieved by an order issued under this

Subchapter by the State rent administrator may file a protest to the State

Commissioner of Housing and Community Renewal in the same manner as provided in
this Subchapter for the filing of a protest against an order of a local rent
administrator. Notes
